WO Mic Privacy
Personal information
We made WO Mic App with your privacy in mind. We do not collect personally identifiable information about you. In other words, we do not collect information such 
					as your name, address, phone number, email address or precise geographic location.
We use below ad networks to serve ads:
Ad Network
Description
Privacy Policy
AdMob
Owned by Google
Google partner policy
Explains for permission requests on Android
In our application, we request some sensitive permissions to make the app work properly:
android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO: to use microphone to record voice as the main feature of the app described
android.permission.BLUETOOTH: To use Bluetooth to transfer voice data
android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN: To turn on Bluetooth automatically if you choose Bluetooth as transport
android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE: Check if Wifi is ON and query acquired IP when Wifi is chosen
android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE: To turn on Wifi automatically if you choose Wifi as transport
android.permission.INTERNET: To do network communication between phone and computer for voice data transfer.
android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE: To check network state for voice data transfer.
android.permission.WAKE_LOCK: To prevent phone into lock state if voice data streaming is going on.
android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION: Get coarse location for ad purpose.
