WO Password Privacy
Personal information
We made WO Password App with your privacy in mind, so we do not collect personally identifiable information about you. In other words, we do not collect information such as your name, 
					address, phone number, email address or precise geographic location.
Explains for permission requests
In our application, we request some permissions to make the app work properly:
android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: to import accounts from file.
android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: to export accounts into file.
